  "abstracts": [
    {
      "note": "summary",
      "abstract": "Provides that the statute of limitations for second-degree sexual assault shall be 10 years from the date of the offense, or, in the case of a victim who is under the age of 18, ten years from the victim\u2019s eighteenth birthday, whichever is later."
